# Project Structure

Overview of the project's directory structure.

## Root Directory
- `backend/`: ActionHero server application
- `frontend/`: Next.js frontend application
- `.cursor/`: Cursor IDE configuration
- `docker-compose.yml`: Docker configuration

## Backend Structure
- `actions/`: API endpoints and CLI commands
- `classes/`: Core ActionHero classes
- `config/`: Server configuration
- `initializers/`: Startup initialization code
- `middleware/`: Action middleware
- `servers/`: Transport implementations (HTTP, WebSocket)
- `types/`: TypeScript type definitions
- `util/`: Utility functions
- `drizzle/`: Database ORM configuration
- `schema/`: Database schemas
- `migrations.ts`: Database migration script

## Frontend Structure
- Next.js application structure
- Separate from backend for independent deployment
